data.description: This well-maintained, spacious 5 bedroom, 2.5 bath raised ranch on almost half an acre lot is conveniently located with easy access to area colleges, UMass, and other area amenities. Main level offers a beautiful eat-in kitchen with granite counters, marble tile backsplash, & island; spacious dining & living room combo with hardwood floors, lots of natural light, fireplace with pellet stove insert, & a slider to a large deck overlooking private backyard; 4 good size bedrooms with closets, one of the bedrooms has an en suite full bathroom; family room; and main full bath with a tub. The lower level offers one more bedroom with a closet; half bath with the laundry hook ups; spacious home office or a hobby shop with a pellet stove and separate interior & exterior access; and a large 2-car garage. HOA in-ground pool is in walking distance behind the house. Dont miss this one!
